WITH LocallyFundedSchools AS (
    SELECT 
        schools.School, 
        schools.DOCType, 
        (frpm.`Enrollment (K-12)` - frpm.`Enrollment (Ages 5-17)`) AS diff
    FROM 
        schools
    INNER JOIN 
        frpm 
    ON 
        schools.CDSCode = frpm.CDSCode
    WHERE 
        schools.FundingType = 'Locally Funded'
),
AverageDifference AS (
    SELECT 
        AVG(diff) AS avg_diff
    FROM 
        LocallyFundedSchools
),
FilteredSchools AS (
    SELECT 
        School, 
        DOCType
    FROM 
        LocallyFundedSchools, AverageDifference
    WHERE 
        LocallyFundedSchools.diff > AverageDifference.avg_diff
)
SELECT 
    School, 
    DOCType
FROM 
    FilteredSchools;	----- bird -----	california_schools

        COUNT(*) AS combination_count

    INNER JOIN

),
most_common_combination AS (

330:
WITH hydrogen_atoms AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT atom.molecule_id
    FROM atom
    WHERE atom.element = 'h'
),
triple_bonded_hydrogen AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT molecule.molecule_id
    FROM molecule
    INNER JOIN atom ON molecule.molecule_id = atom.molecule_id
    INNER JOIN connected ON atom.atom_id = connected.atom_id
    INNER JOIN bond ON connected.bond_id = bond.bond_id
    WHERE atom.element = 'h' AND bond.bond_type = '#' AND molecule.label = '+'
)
SELECT 
    CAST(COUNT(DISTINCT triple_bonded_hydrogen.molecule_id) AS REAL) * 100.0 / COUNT(DISTINCT hydrogen_atoms.molecule_id) AS percentage
FROM 
    hydrogen_atoms
LEFT JOIN triple_bonded_hydrogen ON hydrogen_atoms.molecule_id = triple_bonded_hydrogen.molecule_id;	----- bird -----	toxicology

WITH HighestPlayer AS (
    SELECT 
        Player.player_api_id, 
        Player.player_name, 
        Player.height
    FROM 
        Player
    WHERE 
        Player.height = (SELECT MAX(Player.height) FROM Player)
),
ShortestPlayer AS (
    SELECT 
        Player.player_api_id, 
        Player.player_name, 
        Player.height
    FROM 
        Player
    WHERE 
        Player.height = (SELECT MIN(Player.height) FROM Player)
),
HighestPlayerFinishing AS (
    SELECT 
        AVG(Player_Attributes.finishing) AS avg_finishing
    FROM 
        Player_Attributes
    INNER JOIN 
        HighestPlayer
    ON 
        Player_Attributes.player_api_id = HighestPlayer.player_api_id
),
ShortestPlayerFinishing AS (
    SELECT 
        AVG(Player_Attributes.finishing) AS avg_finishing
    FROM 
        Player_Attributes
    INNER JOIN 
        ShortestPlayer
    ON 
        Player_Attributes.player_api_id = ShortestPlayer.player_api_id
)
SELECT 
    Player.player_name
FROM 
    Player
WHERE 
    Player.player_api_id = (
        SELECT 
            CASE 
                WHEN HighestPlayerFinishing.avg_finishing > ShortestPlayerFinishing.avg_finishing THEN HighestPlayer.player_api_id
                ELSE ShortestPlayer.player_api_id
            END
        FROM 
            HighestPlayerFinishing, ShortestPlayerFinishing
    );	----- bird -----	european_football_2

WITH AgeFiltered AS (
    SELECT 
        Patient.ID AS PatientID
    FROM 
        Patient
    WHERE 
        (strftime('%Y', 'now') - strftime('%Y', Patient.Birthday)) > 55
),
PTFiltered AS (
    SELECT 
        Laboratory.ID AS PatientID
    FROM 
        Laboratory
    WHERE 
        Laboratory.PT >= 14
),
FemaleFiltered AS (
    SELECT 
        Patient.ID AS PatientID
    FROM 
        Patient
    WHERE 
        Patient.SEX = 'F'
),
AbnormalPT AS (
    SELECT 
        AgeFiltered.PatientID
    FROM 
        AgeFiltered
        INNER JOIN PTFiltered ON AgeFiltered.PatientID = PTFiltered.PatientID
),
FemaleAbnormalPT AS (
    SELECT 
        AbnormalPT.PatientID
    FROM 
        AbnormalPT
        INNER JOIN FemaleFiltered ON AbnormalPT.PatientID = FemaleFiltered.PatientID
)
SELECT 
    CAST(COUNT(FemaleAbnormalPT.PatientID) AS REAL) * 100.0 / COUNT(AbnormalPT.PatientID) AS Percentage
FROM 
    AbnormalPT
    LEFT JOIN FemaleAbnormalPT ON AbnormalPT.PatientID = FemaleAbnormalPT.PatientID;	----- bird -----	thrombosis_prediction

WITH FilteredYearMonth AS (
    SELECT 
        yearmonth.CustomerID, 
        yearmonth.Consumption, 
        customers.Segment
    FROM 
        yearmonth
    INNER JOIN 
        customers 
    ON 
        yearmonth.CustomerID = customers.CustomerID
    WHERE 
        SUBSTR(yearmonth.Date, 1, 4) = '2013' -- Filter for year 2013
),
SegmentLowestConsumption AS (
    SELECT 
        Segment, 
        MIN(Consumption) AS LowestConsumption
    FROM 
        FilteredYearMonth
    WHERE 
        customers.Currency = 'CZK' -- Filter for currency CZK
    GROUP BY 
        Segment
),
AnnualAverageConsumption AS (
    SELECT 
        Segment, 
        SUM(LowestConsumption) AS TotalConsumption, 
        COUNT(*) AS CustomerCount
    FROM 
        SegmentLowestConsumption
    GROUP BY 
        Segment
),
Differences AS (
    SELECT 
        'SME-LAM' AS DifferenceType, 
        (SME.TotalConsumption / SME.CustomerCount) - (LAM.TotalConsumption / LAM.CustomerCount) AS Difference
    FROM 
        AnnualAverageConsumption SME
    INNER JOIN 
        AnnualAverageConsumption LAM 
    ON 
        SME.Segment = 'SME' AND LAM.Segment = 'LAM'
    UNION ALL
    SELECT 
        'LAM-KAM' AS DifferenceType, 
        (LAM.TotalConsumption / LAM.CustomerCount) - (KAM.TotalConsumption / KAM.CustomerCount) AS Difference
    FROM 
        AnnualAverageConsumption LAM
    INNER JOIN 
        AnnualAverageConsumption KAM 
    ON 
        LAM.Segment = 'LAM' AND KAM.Segment = 'KAM'
    UNION ALL
    SELECT 
        'KAM-SME' AS DifferenceType, 
        (KAM.TotalConsumption / KAM.CustomerCount) - (SME.TotalConsumption / SME.CustomerCount) AS Difference
    FROM 
        AnnualAverageConsumption KAM
    INNER JOIN 
        AnnualAverageConsumption SME 
    ON 
        KAM.Segment = 'KAM' AND SME.Segment = 'SME'
)
SELECT 
    DifferenceType, 
    Difference
FROM 
    Differences;	----- bird -----	debit_card_specializing

WITH Consumption_2012 AS (
    SELECT 
        customers.Segment AS Segment,
        SUM(yearmonth.Consumption) AS TotalConsumption2012
    FROM 
        yearmonth
    INNER JOIN 
        customers
    ON 
        yearmonth.CustomerID = customers.CustomerID
    WHERE 
        yearmonth.Date LIKE '2012%' AND customers.Currency = 'EUR'
    GROUP BY 
        customers.Segment
),
Consumption_2013 AS (
    SELECT 
        customers.Segment AS Segment,
        SUM(yearmonth.Consumption) AS TotalConsumption2013
    FROM 
        yearmonth
    INNER JOIN 
        customers
    ON 
        yearmonth.CustomerID = customers.CustomerID
    WHERE 
        yearmonth.Date LIKE '2013%' AND customers.Currency = 'EUR'
    GROUP BY 
        customers.Segment
),
PercentageIncrease AS (
    SELECT 
        c2012.Segment AS Segment,
        ((c2013.TotalConsumption2013 - c2012.TotalConsumption2012) * 100.0 / c2012.TotalConsumption2012) AS PercentageIncrease
    FROM 
        Consumption_2012 c2012
    INNER JOIN 
        Consumption_2013 c2013
    ON 
        c2012.Segment = c2013.Segment
)
SELECT 
    Segment
FROM 
    PercentageIncrease
WHERE 
    PercentageIncrease = (SELECT MAX(PercentageIncrease) FROM PercentageIncrease)
UNION
SELECT 
    Segment
FROM 
    PercentageIncrease
WHERE 
    PercentageIncrease = (SELECT MIN(PercentageIncrease) FROM PercentageIncrease);	----- bird -----	debit_card_specializing

WITH customer_id_cte AS (
    SELECT 
        t1.CustomerID
    FROM 
        transactions_1k AS t1
    WHERE 
        t1.Date = '2012-08-25' AND t1.Price = 634.8
),
consumption_2012 AS (
    SELECT 
        ym.CustomerID,
        SUM(ym.Consumption) AS total_consumption_2012
    FROM 
        yearmonth AS ym
    WHERE 
        ym.Date LIKE '2012%'
    GROUP BY 
        ym.CustomerID
),
consumption_2013 AS (
    SELECT 
        ym.CustomerID,
        SUM(ym.Consumption) AS total_consumption_2013
    FROM 
        yearmonth AS ym
    WHERE 
        ym.Date LIKE '2013%'
    GROUP BY 
        ym.CustomerID
)
SELECT 
    CAST(
        (c2012.total_consumption_2012 - c2013.total_consumption_2013) AS REAL
    ) / c2012.total_consumption_2012 AS consumption_decrease_rate
FROM 
    customer_id_cte AS cid
INNER JOIN 
    consumption_2012 AS c2012
ON 
    cid.CustomerID = c2012.CustomerID
INNER JOIN 
    consumption_2013 AS c2013
ON 
    cid.CustomerID = c2013.CustomerID;	----- bird -----	debit_card_specializing

WITH TopSpendingCustomer AS (
    SELECT 
        c.CustomerID,
        c.Currency,
        SUM(t.Price) / SUM(t.Amount) AS AveragePricePerItem,
        SUM(t.Amount) AS TotalSpending
    FROM 
        customers AS c
    INNER JOIN 
        transactions_1k AS t
    ON 
        c.CustomerID = t.CustomerID
    GROUP BY 
        c.CustomerID, c.Currency
    ORDER BY 
        TotalSpending DESC
    LIMIT 1
)
SELECT 
    CustomerID,
    Currency,
    AveragePricePerItem
FROM 
    TopSpendingCustomer;	----- bird -----	debit_card_specializing
